rows.label: qst200811_0010
rows.name:
Sorry to keep you waiting.
I'll heal you now.

rows.label: qst200811_0020
rows.name: How is it? Does it look like it'll heal?

rows.label: qst200811_0030
rows.name:
...Yes, it's alright. I think she will
gradually regain her strength with this.

rows.label: qst200811_0040
rows.name: I see. Then we can rest easy now.

rows.label: qst200811_0060
rows.name:
Yes. I'm sure this child
is saying thank you too.

rows.label: qst200811_0080
rows.name:
Even if it's just a tree, it's
a relief to know it's safe.

rows.label: qst200811_0090
rows.name:
Of course. They are all
living just like us.

rows.label: qst200811_0100
rows.name:
I learned something from
you this time, Hotaru...
